{"tid":1020494,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲玩【Spellbreak】？","createTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T05:04:59.000Z","uid":45533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c58adc3214b60b41220281751f3074e62e84126d","tid":1020494,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"Spellbreak簡單黎講就係<span style=\"color: violet;\">玩魔法既食雞</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近開始係Epic Game上左架，但都仲係封測緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">玩法</span></span><br />\n一開始等齊20人先開始 倒數緊既時候執既野game start個時係會reset<br />\n如果玩squad 一開始4個玩家揀地點降落<br />\n之後都係不外乎執item殺人 當然最重要係執<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>魔法拳套</strong></span>先打到交 左右手各一隻<br />\n魔法有6種屬性：<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span> <span style=\"color: teal;\">冰</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">雷</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">風</span> <span style=\"color: brown;\">地</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">毒</span><br />\nitem有幾種稀有度 <span style=\"color: pink;\">白色</span>最cheap <span style=\"color: orange;\">橙色</span>最rare 白&gt;綠&gt;藍&gt;紫&gt;橙 好似係<br />\n至於點樣combo同玩法 就要自己摸索 呢到唔多講 有興趣可以睇多d gameplay<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">玩家Gameplay：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIRrP2Ts5cw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUIRrP2Ts5cw&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyESK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=451300ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UIRrP2Ts5cw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">點樣申請呀？</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">官網：</span><a href=\"https://playspellbreak.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplayspellbreak.com%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyESK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=26cd273a\" target=\"_blank\">https://playspellbreak.com/</a><br />\n係官網用email sign up，如果成功會有email俾條key你係Epic Game dl玩<br />\nbtw <span style=\"color: violet;\">How did you get to this form?</span>個到如果鍾意可以寫我個discord <span style=\"color: violet;\">Amy#9160</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">官方discord：</span><a href=\"https://discordapp.com/invite/proletariat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2Finvite%2Fproletariat&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyESK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=48fa20fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/invite/proletariat</a><br />\n<br />\n我睇一次開遊戲post 希望大家手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果大家有資料/技巧share歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64de4ce8f07ae86264a9f90a2b06ccd3ffcb1d31","tid":1020494,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"訓前一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be154e3affa96fc38660bc58daa5a49c1ee63652","tid":1020494,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:17:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8374c27a32988da726b6baaeda4d201ee805071a","tid":1020494,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7b3569099fbd3bc7719039b6379f09dfc01c4a","tid":1020494,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"玩緊apex呀 死開啦"},{"pid":"42fa464208d946c5fe71019ce73cb67f28677905","tid":1020494,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"89dfb571a9bc08e2bba3f4706e090f0b95bf13db","tid":1020494,"uid":45533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7b3569099fbd3bc771903